OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fthe odd spot of light rain possible
OL,7,Faround eastern coasts, but
OL,8,Fpredominately dry. A dry afternoon
OL,9,Fwith cloud breaking up to allow bright
OL,10,Fand sunny spells to break through.
OL,11,FLight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with some sunny spells at
OL,14,Ffirst but generally turning cloudier
OL,15,Fthrough the evening. Remaining largely
OL,16,Fdry and cloudy overnight with some
OL,17,Fclearer intervals, these mostly in the
OL,18,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
