OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry start with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Any cloud gradually breaking
OL,7,Fup through the day to give largely
OL,8,Fclear skies and plenty of sunshine in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Warmer than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Flargely dry and settled few days with
OL,13,Fthe odd spot of rain possible at
OL,14,Ftimes. Cloudy at times but still
OL,15,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells on
OL,16,Foffer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
